      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Heading -->
    <div class="mb-8 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-light-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        <span class="text-light-900">
          Starte deine
        </span>
        <br>
        <span class="text-light-600">Transformation</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Description -->
    <div class="mb-12 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-light-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Lade LoopCut kostenlos herunter und beginne noch heute damit, deine 
        <span class="text-light-500 font-medium">Gedanken in kraftvolle ZukunftsplÃ¤ne zu verwandeln.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Features List -->
    <div class="mb-12 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-4 text-light-700">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-light-700 rounded-full"></div>
          <span>Kostenloser Download</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
